data.description: REDUCED $20,000!!!  Charming totally redone 2 bedroom and 2 bath ranch just north of all the Hamilton Heights schools! The third bedroom was made into a huge walk in closet for the primary bedroom! Huge fenced in backyard with a nice new deck! Big covered front porch! All stainless steel smooth top stove and refrigerator. Washer and dryer are negotiable. Updated plumbing, electrical, paint and flooring throughout! Mature trees!
